  "title": "ITSM Manager - Release Management (Permanent | Onsite)",
  "description": "<p>We are hiring an experienced <strong>ITSM Release Manager</strong> to manage and govern technology releases supporting mission-critical systems in a highly regulated environment. This role focuses on ensuring safe, compliant, and low-risk deployments into production.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Plan, coordinate, and govern end-to-end technology releases</li><li>Manage release calendars, dependencies, risks, and approvals</li><li>Chair release review meetings and ensure readiness for go-live</li><li>Work closely with engineering, QA, operations, and external teams</li><li>Ensure segregation of duties and adherence to release policies</li><li>Track release KPIs, risks, and post-implementation reviews</li><li>Drive continuous improvement across release management processes</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in IT, Computer Science, or related discipline</li><li>Minimum 3 years’ hands-on experience in IT Release Management</li><li>Strong knowledge of ITIL / ITSM, SDLC, Agile / DevOps practices</li><li>Experience with tools such as ServiceNow, JIRA, Git, CI/CD pipelines</li><li>Comfortable managing multiple concurrent releases</li><li>Strong stakeholder communication and coordination skills</li><li>ITIL 4 certification preferred</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, please submit your updated resume in MS format by using the Apply Now Button. Alternatively, you may also email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:friedachan@careerally.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">friedachan@careerally.com.sg</a></p><p>We regret that only short-listed candidates will be contacted shortly.</p><p>Careerally Pte Ltd | EA Licence: 24C2215<br />Frieda Chan | EA Registration No: R2199193</p>",
